A lot of this stuff is just what you pick up along the way, and you don't
have to be a pro to know about it. Just look at me :) You can probably
learn these things in 3-4 months, if you stick with it evenings and 
weekends. Buy a good book (do you read the book reviews in EDM/2;
available at ftp.cdrom.com in pub/os2/32bit/program/newsltr or something
similar), and follow it all the way through. Then pick up a more advanced
book, and really start. Good luck.

